0happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20try%20to%20get%20a%20refund%20on%20your%20hotel%20stay%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20make%20the%20housekeeper%20unsee%20your%20bare%20butt.%20Deadbolt%20your%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIgnore%20hotel%20policies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20reasonable%2C%20considerate%20person%2C%20chances%20are%20you're%20probably%20already%20pretty%20compliant%20with%20hotel%20policies%20%E2%80%94%20no%20excessive%20noise%2C%20no%20smoking%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20hotels%20have%20considerable%20monetary%20penalties%20for%20breaking%20these%20policies%2C%20so%20it%20could%20cost%20you%20hundreds%20(if%20not%20thousands)%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20hotel%20likely%20already%20has%20your%20credit-card%20information%20on%20file%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20charging%20you.%20Plus%2C%20you%20probably%20signed%20a%20waiver%20when%20you%20first%20checked%20in%2C%20agreeing%20to%20pay%20that%20money%20if%20you%20failed%20to%20comply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESettle%20in%20before%20inspecting%20my%20room%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221829%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22view%20of%20wheely%20suitcase%20inside%20a%20bright%20hotel%20room%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579f86c50edbc52a863daca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221372%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20check%20for%20safety%2C%20cleanliness%2C%20and%20functionality%20before%20unpacking%20my%20bags.%20%3Cp%3Eluchunyu%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20most%20people%20realize%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20and%20stress%20that%20doing%20a%20quick%20inspection%20of%20your%20hotel%20room%20can%20save%20you%20(and%20the%20hotel%20staff).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20forget%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftiktoker-internet-divided-sharing-hotel-room-cleaning-routine-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeck%20the%20room's%20cleanliness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20make%20sure%20the%20hot%20water%20and%20HVAC%20systems%20work%2C%20or%20test%20the%20function%20of%20any%20electronics%20(TV%2C%20lamp%2C%20alarm%20clock).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20way%20better%20to%20identify%20these%20problems%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20and%20get%20the%20hotel%20staff%20to%20solve%20them%20before%20you've%20settled%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20at%20several%20different%20hotels%20instead%20of%20joining%20a%20loyalty%20program%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20anyone%20who%20doesn't%20love%20spending%20points%20instead%20of%20money%2C%20and%20I'm%20consistently%20shocked%20at%20how%20quickly%20my%20hotel%20loyalty%20points%20rack%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20earned%20countless%20free%20nights%20and%20gift%20cards%20from%20traveling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20just%20booking%20with%20different%20hotels%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20definitely%20worth%20it%20to%20join%20a%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20membership%20can%20also%20get%20you%20certain%20privileges%2C%20like%20free%20late%20checkouts.%20Plus%20the%20staff%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20give%20you%20a%20free%20room%20upgrade%20or%20other%20perks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EToss%20aside%20the%20'do%20not%20disturb'%20signs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22exterior%20of%20a%20hotel%20room%20door%20with%20a%20please%20do%20not%20disturb%20sign%20hanging%20on%20the%20handle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579f7c67a3c8094d5dc9cee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221380%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20save%20time%20and%20resources%20by%20using%20the%20do-not-disturb%20sign.%3Cp%3EDragon%20Images%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20do-not-disturb%20sign%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20prevent%20hotel%20staff%20from%20bothering%20you.%20But%20it's%20not%20just%20for%20privacy%20%E2%80%94%20it%20also%20reduces%20unnecessary%20housekeeping%20services%2C%20which%20promotes%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20you'd%20be%20lightening%20the%20workload%20of%20the%20housekeepers%2C%20which%20is%20something%20you%20can%20feel%20good%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthings-never-do-at-hotel-from-frequent-guest-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estay%20at%20a%20hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20keep%20track%20of%20the%20door-hanging%20sign%20and%20put%20it%20out%20whenever%20I%20don't%20need%20a%20refresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBook%20without%20confirming%20the%20amenities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20read%20hotel%20reviews%2C%20but%20a%20surprising%20number%20of%20people%20forget%20to%20check%20if%20the%20hotel%20actually%20has%20all%20the%20amenities%20they're%20expecting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fluxury-five-star-hotels-most-surprising-things-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehotel's%20star%20ranking%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20necessarily%20reflect%20the%20reviews%20of%20their%20guests%20%E2%80%94%20rather%2C%20it's%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20amenities%20they%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20two-star%20hotel%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20pool%2C%20spa%2C%20restaurant%2C%20or%20room%20service%2C%20so%20keep%20this%20in%20mind%20when%20choosing%20a%20place%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeave%20without%20checking%20out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20importance%20of%20the%20check-out%20procedure%20seems%20to%20have%20slipped%20from%20people's%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20the%20process%20is%20straightforward%20%E2%80%94%20it%20signals%20to%20the%20hotel%20staff%20that%20you've%20left%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20initiate%20the%20preparation%20of%20your%20room%20for%20the%20next%20guest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20guests%20don't%20bother%20to%20check%20out%2C%20the%20staff%20must%20physically%20visit%20each%20room%20to%20ensure%20it's%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20days%20when%20I%20found%20myself%20running%20through%20the%20entire%20hotel%2C%20inspecting%2050-plus%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-former-employee-would-never-do-at-a-hotel-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702563384000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579f7e750edbc52a863da64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-former-employee-would-never-do-at-a-hotel-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20worked%20at%20a%20popular%20hotel%20chain%20for%20three%20years%2C%20and%20it%20definitely%20changed%20the%20way%20I%20travel.%20Now%2C%20I%20always%20deadbolt%20the%20door%20and%20inspect%20my%20room.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(%20Dani%20Quesnel%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-former-employee-would-never-do-at-a-hotel-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20nightmare%20for%20repairs%20and%20insurance%2C%20experts%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cybertruck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656619e3c58b6f84123af453%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20won't%20know%20the%20details%20of%20how%20to%20repair%20Tesla's%20Cybertruck%20until%20there%20are%20more%20than%20a%20few%20on%20the%20road.%3Cp%3ETesla%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20claims%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-truck-cybertruck%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20Cybertruck%3C%2Fa%3E's%20hard%20surface%20is%20so%20damage-resistant%20that%20it%20can%20stop%20bullets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20stainless%20steel%20body%20panels%20may%20be%20a%20huge%20drawback%2C%C2%A0auto%20body%20experts%20and%20insurance%20agents%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20originally%20appeared%20on%20InsideEVs.com%20and%20was%20republished%20with%20permission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20has%20delivered%20on%20his%20promise%20to%20get%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F698764%2Ftesla-cybertruck-delivery-specs-power-range-price%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20Cybertruck%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20production.%20The%20wedge-shaped%2C%20Syd%20Mead%20meets%20Giorgetto%20Giugiaro%20design%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-in-person-surprisingly-different-up-close-2023-12%23one-tesla-employee-said-the-cybertruck-was-too-expensive-17%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eout%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20albeit%20with%20some%20design%20concessions%20from%20the%20concept%20version%20to%20make%20the%20whole%20package%20work.%20It%20might%20not%20go%20as%20far%20as%20originally%20promised%2C%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F698701%2Ftesla-cybertruck-official-price%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20expensive%20than%20he%20originally%20said%20it%20would%20be%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20Cybertruck%20still%20looks%20very%20close%20to%20the%20concept%20Musk%20surprised%20us%20with%20back%20in%202019%E2%80%94stainless%20steel%20body%20panels%20and%20all.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20stainless%20steel%20body%20panels%20might%20be%20one%20of%20the%20truck's%20biggest%20draws%2C%20but%20could%20they%20be%20its%20Achilles%20heel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20and%20Tesla%20claim%20that%20the%20truck's%20hard%20surface%20is%20so%20damage-resistant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F698778%2Ftesla-cybertruck-stop-bullets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20it%20can%20stop%20bullets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20like%20every%20material%20in%20the%20known%20physical%20realm%2C%20it%20can%20be%20broken.%20And%20when%20something%20gets%20broken%2C%20it'll%20need%20to%20be%20repaired.%20That's%20where%20things%20get%20tricky%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20there%20are%20only%20about%20a%20baker's%20dozen's%20worth%20of%20production%20Cybertrucks%20on%20the%20road.%20Coupled%20with%20Tesla's%20notoriously%20rigorous%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musks-tesla-suing-an-ex-worker-who-it-says-downloaded-trade-secrets-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etight-lipped%20stance%20toward%20its%20trade%20secrets%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20repairability%2C%20we%20won't%20know%20the%20explicit%2C%20granular%20details%20of%20how%20to%20repair%20the%20Cybertruck%20until%20there%20are%20more%20than%20a%20few%20on%20the%20road%2C%20and%20rumblings%20about%20the%20truck%20in%20private%2C%20go%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cybertruck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6538fe290487ff031cadab79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221447%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20that%20the%20Cybertruck%20would%20start%20at%20%2439%2C900%20when%20he%20unveiled%20it%20in%202019.%3Cp%3EFrederic%20J.%20Brown%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20we%20all%20have%20eyes.%20The%20Cybertruck%20isn't%20the%20first%20electric%20truck%2C%20not%20the%20first%20Tesla%2C%20and%20not%20the%20first%20vehicle%20to%20be%20made%20of%20stainless%20steel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-owners-first-deliveries-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECybetruck%20owners%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20be%20in%20for%20when%20the%20going%20gets%20tough%20for%20their%20trucks%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20a%20few%20sources%20familiar%20with%20autobody%20repair%2C%20stainless%20steel%20repair%2C%20fixing%20Teslas%20specifically%2C%20and%20other%20people%20with%20expert%20knowledge%20in%20this%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20picture%20they%20painted%20is%20cautiously%20optimistic%20at%20best%2C%20but%20also%20earnest%20about%20the%20challenges%20the%20truck's%20design%20presents.%20And%20those%20experts%20are%20adamant%20about%20how%20the%20truck%20could%20further%20test%20the%20often-contentious%20relationships%20between%20the%20consumer%2C%20auto%20body%20technicians%20and%20the%20insurance%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStainless%20steel%20is%20hard%20to%20repair%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cybertruck%20is%20unusually%20stiff.%20Its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F654590%2Ftesla-cybertruck-hard-cold-rolled-steel-patent-musk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3mm%20thick%20stainless%20steel%20panels%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20undoubtedly%20an%20industry%20first.%20Musk%20bragged%20that%20traditional%20auto%20presses%2C%20which%20can%20exert%20literal%20tons%20of%20force%2C%20can't%20even%20shape%20the%20stuff%20because%20it's%20so%20thick%20and%20hard.%20It's%20silly%20to%20expect%20that%20a%20standard%20PDR%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dentheads.com%2Fabout-us%2Fblog%2Fentryid%2F14%2Fhow-paintless-dent-repair-works%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520paintless%2520dent%2520repair%252C%2520a%2Cdamage%2520to%2520your%2520vehicle%2527s%2520paint.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaintless%20dent%20removal%3C%2Fa%3E)%20guy%20could%20use%20their%20tools%20to%20hammer%20out%20any%20dents.%20Yet%2C%20not%20considering%20the%20Cybertruck's%20proprietary%20metal%20alloy%20and%20absurd%20thickness%2C%20we%20already%20have%20at%20least%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20precedent%20of%20how%20to%20repair%20stainless%20steel%20%E2%80%94%20an%20example%20from%20the%201980s%2C%20when%20DeLoreans%20were%20still%20new%20and%20probably%20more%20on%20the%20road%20than%20they%20are%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20labor%20to%20ensure%20the%20body%20panels%20remain%20straight%20and%20usable.%20Then%2C%20unlike%20normal%20car%20steel%20(or%20even%20aluminum)%20body%20panels%2C%20you%20can't%20hide%20structurally%20sound%2C%20but%20visually%20unappealing%2C%20repairs%20behind%20body%20filler%20and%20paint%20since%20the%20trucks%20are%20unpainted.%20So%2C%20every%20repair%20has%20to%20be%20pitch-perfect%2C%20which%20isn't%20easy%2C%20and%2C%20more%20crucially%2C%20very%20time-consuming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Cybertruck%20cordoned%20off%20at%20Tesla's%20Santana%20Row%20showroom%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California%2C%20on%20December%209%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657624b30ec98e92f74df3c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Cybertruck%20at%20Tesla's%20Santana%20Row%20showroom%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EAlistair%20Barr%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20the%20stories%20behind%20painted%20DeLoreans%20often%20come%20from%20accident-involved%20vehicles%3B%20it%20didn't%20make%20any%20financial%20sense%20to%20spend%20hours%20repairing%20a%20stainless%20steel%20panel.%20Instead%2C%20some%20owners%20and%20body%20shop%20guys%20would%20use%20traditional%20techniques%20involving%20body%20filler%2C%20and%20then%20opt%20to%20paint%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRepairing%20stainless%20steel%20is%20a%20novelty%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Josh%20Bengston%2C%20owner%20and%20operator%20of%20DeLorean%20Industries%20in%20Tallmadge%2C%20Ohio.%20His%20company%20repairs%20DMC-12s%20and%20sells%20parts%20for%20them.%20Although%20our%20conversation%20was%20short%2C%20Bengston%20was%20pointed%20and%20direct.%20Repairing%20stainless%20steel%20really%20only%20makes%20sense%20for%20classic%20and%20collector%20cars%20like%20the%20DeLorean%20where%20replacements%20might%20not%20exist%2C%20and%20the%20cars%20themselves%20are%20special%2C%20rare%20items%20for%20hobbyists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20Espey%2C%20president%20of%20another%20shop%2C%20Classic%20DMC%2C%20was%20a%20little%20more%20optimistic.%20But%20he%20agreed%20that%20the%20labor%20to%20repair%20stainless%20steel%20isn't%20easy.%20Espey%20described%20some%20of%20the%20repair%20processes%20of%20DeLorean%20panels%20as%20%26quot%3Bold%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20they're%20using%20pick%20and%20files%2C%20not%20the%20computerized%20body%20shop%20tools%20to%20beat%20out%20divots%20and%20dings.%20It's%20an%20art%20form%20that%20takes%20a%20lot%20more%20time%20than%20the%20average%20steel%20fender.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20going%20to%20spend%20more%20than%20say%2C%20eight%2C%20nine%20hours%20trying%20to%20do%20a%20repair%2C%20you're%20better%20off%20just%20buying%20a%20new%20(panel)%2C%26quot%3B%20Espey%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20concerns%20of%20an%20elevated%20labor%20cost%20were%20shared%20amongst%20a%20Facebook%20group%20full%20of%20novice%20and%20veteran%20auto%20body%20repair%20technicians.%20Sure%2C%20the%20Cybertruck's%20panels%20will%20potentially%20be%20able%20to%20be%20repaired%20like%20DeLoreans%20were%2C%20but%20there's%20the%20big%20question%3A%20will%20insurance%20companies%20approve%20labor-intensive%20repairs%3F%20High%20labor%20totals%20out%20cars%3B%20they're%20why%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F665545%2Frivian-r1t-fender-bender-big-repair-bill%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20Ohio%20driver's%20Rivian%20R1T%20repair%20came%20out%20to%20a%20whopping%20%2442%2C000%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20basic%20fender%20bender.%20High%20repair%20bills%20like%20that%20are%20the%20things%20that%20total%20out%20trucks%2C%20as%20some%20Rivian%20owners%20are%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EReplacing%20panels%20could%20open%20up%20a%20twofold%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReplacing%20panels%20would%20likely%20be%20significantly%20quicker%20(and%20thus%20represent%20lower%20labor%20costs)%20than%20repairing%20them%2C%20insisting%20on%20replacing%20rather%20than%20repairing%20could%20open%20up%20a%20new%20can%20of%20worms.%20Arguably%2C%20it's%20only%20exacerbating%20the%20current%20stress%20points%20Tesla%20owners%20are%20already%20experiencing%20with%20their%20insurance%20companies%3A%20long%20waits%20for%20repair%20times%2C%20and%20high%20repair%20costs%2C%20even%20before%20Tesla's%20controversial%20choice%20to%20go%20with%20stainless%20steel%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cybertruck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65660a74fe5bc6545ebce8db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20has%20finally%20started%20to%20deliver%20the%20first%20few%20Cybertrucks%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3ESUZANNE%20CORDEIRO%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20a%20lot%20of%20customers%20hire%20me%20to%20fight%20insurance%20companies%20because%20insurance%20companies%20do%20not%20want%20to%20pay%20what%20Tesla%20requires%20you%20do%20to%20return%20a%20vehicle%20to%20pre-loss%20condition%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Billy%20Walkowiak%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Collision%20Safety%20Consultants%2C%20a%20firm%20in%20part%20meant%20to%20serve%20as%20an%20advocate%20and%20adjudicator%20for%20insurance%20claimants%20who%20may%20not%20feel%20like%20the%20insurance%20company%20is%20effectively%20making%20them%20whole.%20%26quot%3BI%20personally%20probably%20do%2010%20to%2015%20Teslas%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalkowiak%20explained%20that%20although%20we%20can't%20quite%20yet%20know%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%20with%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20Tesla's%20repair%20procedures%20have%20historically%20skewed%20toward%20replacement%20of%20parts%2C%20rather%20than%20repairing%20parts%20strategy.%20Add%20in%20the%20complicated%20software%20recalibration%20procedures%20and%20elevated%20labor%20costs%E2%80%94only%20Tesla-certified%20technicians%20can%20repair%20Tesla%20vehicles%E2%80%94%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F570075%2Ftesla-modely-collision-repair-advice%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20it%20all%20gets%20expensive%20very%20quickly%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Walkowiak%20shared%20a%20Tesla%20Model%203%20claim%20that%20was%20%2422%2C000%2C%20with%20%2414%2C000%20of%20that%20solely%20being%20replacement%20parts.%20Yikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTesla's%20getting%20challenged%20because%20insurance%20companies%20now%20have%20their%20greedy%20little%20hands%20into%20the%20estimating%20software%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20Walkowiak%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they%20can%20say%20that%20they%20don't%20believe%20it%20needs%20that%20we%20%5Bthe%20body%20shop%20says%5D%20because%20according%20to%20the%20%5Binsurance%20company's%5D%20software%2C%20it%20doesn't%20need%20that%2C%20or%20%5Bthey're%5D%20not%20paying%20for%20that%2C%20or%20that's%20too%20expensive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20the%20replacement%20parts%20strategy%20that%20will%20likely%20apply%20to%20the%20Cybertruck%20could%20create%20a%20new%20problem%3A%20can%20Tesla%20even%20make%20enough%20parts%20to%20keep%20up%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20reading%20stories%20in%20the%20automotive%20trade%20press%20about%20how%20replacement%20parts%20for%20the%20Model%20S%20and%20the%203%20the%20Y%2C%20and%20the%20X%20were%20all%20short%20supply%20items%20because%20they%20were%20building%20everything%20they%20could%20make.%20%5BTesla%5D%20hadn't%20allocated%20enough%20spare%20parts%20is%20how%20I%20understood%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Espey%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20part%20repair%20woes%20have%20gotten%20somewhat%20better%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20all%20that%20hard%20to%20find%20reports%20on%20social%20media%20of%20Tesla%20owners%20upset%20that%20their%20repairs%20take%20a%20long%20time%2C%20with%20wait%20times%20upward%20of%20six%20months.%20%26quot%3BThe%20DeLorean%20company%20was%20really%20good%20about%20making%20every%20dealer%20buy%20a%20certain%20subset%20of%20spare%20parts%2C%20including%20body%20panels%2C%26quot%3B%20Epsey%20said.%20%26quot%3BIs%20every%20Tesla%20service%20center%20going%20to%20have%20body%20panels%20on%20hand%20to%20ship%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20cast%20doubt%20on%20any%20availability%20of%20outside%20OEM%20parts.%20Since%20the%20Cybertruck%20is%20purportedly%20using%20a%20custom%20stainless%20steel%20alloy%2C%20it's%20not%20clear%20if%20third-party%20companies%20will%20be%20able%20to%20create%20aftermarket%20body%20panels%20for%20the%20truck.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESome%20remain%20optimistic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Espey%20wasn't%20all%20doom%20and%20gloom%20on%20the%20Cybertruck.%20Later%20in%20our%20conversation%2C%20he%20compared%20the%20Cybertruck's%20stainless%20steel%20panels%20to%20the%20Ford%20F-150's%20aluminum%20body%E2%80%94something%20that%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjalopnik.com%2Fhow-a-2015-ford-f-150-aluminum-repair-cost-17-000-and-1719664610%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintensely%20controversial%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20first%20came%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there%20are%20some%20lingering%20feelings%20about%20the%20costs%20and%20techniques%20of%20repairing%20an%20aluminum%20car%2C%20but%20by%20and%20large%2C%20the%20auto%20body%20repair%20industry%20has%20adapted.%20(The%20vast%20popularity%20of%20the%20F-150%20has%20a%20way%20of%20doing%20that.)%C2%A0These%20days%2C%20aluminum%20body%20repair%20is%20kind%20of%20a%20non-issue%2C%20although%20some%20body%20shop%20guys%20do%20insist%20the%20elevated%20costs%20associated%20with%20repairing%20them%20are%20still%20very%20much%20an%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20at%20another%20Ohio%20body%20shop%20I%20spoke%20to%20(that%20includes%C2%A0a%207%2C000-square-foot%20dedicated%20EV%20repair%20space)%20were%20more%20optimistic%20too.%20They%20insisted%C2%A0Tesla%20usually%20gives%20out%20good%20training%20on%20how%20to%20repair%20its%20vehicles%2C%20a%20sentiment%20seconded%20by%20other%20industry%20professionals%20I%20surveyed%20for%20this%20story.%20It's%20very%20possible%20the%20automaker%20%E2%80%94%20which%20does%20not%20speak%20to%20the%20press%20in%20America%20%E2%80%94%20has%20a%20plan%20for%20repairs%20that%20we're%20not%20privy%20to%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20collision%20repair%20involves%20more%20than%20just%20the%20physical%20act%20of%20pulling%20out%20a%20dent%20and%20paying%20a%20body%20shop%20guy.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20moving%20pieces%20at%20work%20here%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20clear%20how%20the%20Cybertruck%20will%20fare%20when%20the%20chips%20fall%20where%20they%20may.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20Delivery%20Event%20(2023)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.motor1.com%2Fimages%2Fstatic%2F16x9-tr.png%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20in%20showroom%20(source%3A%20Out%20of%20Spec%20Reviews)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.motor1.com%2Fimages%2Fstatic%2F16x9-tr.png%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.motor1.com%2Fimages%2Fstatic%2F16x9-tr.png%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20