%20country's%20output%2C%20and%20typically%20generate%20more%20sales%20and%20profits%20when%20the%20economy%20is%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20recession%20risk%20at%20all%20embedded%20in%20equity%20valuations%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20said%20in%20a%20research%20note%20on%20Thursday%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20he%20believes%20stock%20investors%20are%20too%20optimistic%20about%20what's%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%20also%20cautioned%20on%20X%20that%20the%20Fed's%20forecast%20of%20slower%20GDP%20growth%20next%20year%20implies%20a%2090%25%20probability%20of%20recession.%20He%20explained%20that%20his%20team%20expects%20inflation%20to%20plummet%20below%201%25%20next%20year%2C%20making%203.8%25%20nominal%20growth%20%26quot%3Bvery%20difficult%20to%20achieve%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20closer%20to%202%25%20more%20realistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20my%20lens%2C%20given%20what%20the%20monetary%20policy%20lags%20imply%20and%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20fiscal%20stimulus%20means%20for%20real%20GDP%20growth%20for%202024%2C%20we%20are%20likely%20talking%20about%20real%20growth%20of%20no%20better%20than%20%2B1.0%25%20and%20quite%20possibly%20zero%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20note%20to%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20rare%20but%20not%20unprecedented%3A%20we%20saw%20this%20in%201949%2C%201954%2C%201958%2C%202008%2C%20and%202009%20%E2%80%94%20all%20recessions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20the%20odds%20are%20100%25%20instead%20of%2090%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20delayed%20in%202023%20shall%20not%20be%20derailed%20in%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%20has%20been%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20on%20a%20stock-market%20crash%20and%20recession%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-risks-charts-extreme-euphoric-conditions-david-rosenberg-2021-2%5C%22%3Efor%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20going%20as%20far%20as%20comparing%20the%20current%20situ