ed%20staff%20of%20negligence%20for%20failing%20to%20secure%20the%20freezer%20and%20not%20conducting%20a%20thorough%20search%20when%20Jenkins%20first%20went%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20out%20of%20a%20total%20settlement%20of%20%2410%20million%2C%20some%20%243.5%20million%20will%20go%20toward%20legal%20fees.%20Ms%20Martin%20will%20receive%20more%20than%20%243.7%20million%2C%20and%20two%20other%20relatives%20will%20receive%20%241.5%20million%20and%20%241.2%20million.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702557540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fflbos4v_kenneka-jenkins_625x300_14_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffamily-of-us-teen-who-died-in-hotel-freezer-to-get-more-than-6-million-in-settlement-4673496%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teen%20was%20found%20in%20a%20freezer%20in%20an%20unused%20kitchen%20at%20Crowne%20Plaza%20Chicago%20O'Hare%20Hotel%20in%20Rosemont%2C%20where%20she%20had%20gone%20to%20a%20late-night%20party%20in%20September%202017.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffamily-of-us-teen-who-died-in-hotel-freezer-to-get-more-than-6-million-in-settlement-4673496%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffamily-of-us-teen-who-died-in-hotel-freezer-to-get-more-than-6-million-in-settlement-4673496%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffamily-of-us-teen-who-died-in-hotel-freezer-to-get-more-than-6-million-in-settlement-4673496%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thieves%20In%20US%20Plead%20For%20Lesser%20Punishment%20Arguing%20They%20Stole%20Items%20On%20Sale%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20thieves%20in%20Colorado%2C%20United%20States%2C%20were%20convicted%20of%20theft%20for%20stealing%20goods%20worth%20%242000%20from%20a%20departmenta