20enemy%20by%20creating%20a%20smoke%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20canisters%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20used%20as%20attention-seeking%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ones%20used%20in%20the%20intrusion%20carried%20the%20marking%20%26quot%3BCreative%20Colour%20Smoke%26quot%3B%20-%20very%20easily%20available%20on%20the%20internet%20and%20cost%20just%20about%20Rs%2075%20apiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20website%20selling%20these%20online%20advertises%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20for%20showcasing%20visuals%20and%20photography%2C%20as%20well%20as%20costume%20parties%20and%20Halloween%20decorations.%20Suitable%20for%20stage%2C%20movie%2C%20advertisement%2C%20TV%2C%20drama%20and%20other%20scenes.%20It%20produces%20a%20solid-coloured%20smoke%20effect.%20100%25%20brand%20new%2C%20quality%20assured%2C%20safe%20to%20use.%20It's%20the%20number%20one%20choice%20for%20film%2C%20TV%2C%20commercials%2C%20commercials%20and%20digital%20photography!%20Easy%20to%20use%2C%20just%20open%20the%20pull%20tab%20to%20use%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cabinet%20Minister%2C%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThankfully%20these%20were%20just%20smoke%20bombs.%20What%20if%20they%20were%20lethal%20chemical%20explosives%3F%20The%20results%20could%20have%20been%20horrendous.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20intrusion%20exposed%20a%20big%20chink%20in%20the%20parliament's%20security%20armour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20smoke%20bombs%20usually%20do%20not%20have%20any%20metal%20pieces%20and%20do%20not%20set%20off%20the%20metal%20detectors.%20The%20potassium%20nitrate%20could%20have%20been%20detected%20by%20odour%20detectors%20-%20the%20hand-held%20sniffing%20devices%20routinely%20used%20by%20the%20security%20personnel%20at%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan.%20A%20modified%20version%20of%20this%20is%20used%20at%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20suggest%20that%20sniffer%20dogs%20could%20also%20have%20detected%20the%20potassium%20nitrate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202020%20advisory%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20on%20'augmentation%20of%20K9s'%20lists%20the%20detection%20of%20acid%20salts%20like%20potassium%20nitrate%20as%20an%20essential%20requirement%20for%20trained%20dog%20squads.%20Sniffer%20dogs%20do%20a%20great%20job%20detecting%20explosives%20and%20on%20his%20visit%20to%20India%2C%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20security%20detail%20used%20them%20to%20scan%20the%20media's%20camera%20equipment%20at%20his%20press%20conference%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20oxidiser%20in%20these%20canisters%20is%20a%20very%20commonly%20available%20chemical%20called%20potassium%20nitrate%20or%20saltpetre%20which%20is%20widely%20used%20as%20a%20fertiliser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20packed%20in%20large%20quantities%2C%20potassium%20nitrate%20can%20be%20used%20in%20explosive%20devices%20such%20as%20improvised%20explosive%20devices%2C%20or%20IEDs.%20The%20infamous%201995%20Oklahoma%20City%20bombing%20in%20the%20US%20used%20a%20truckload%20of%20potassium%20nitrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fuel%20used%20in%20these%20canisters%20is%20finely%20ground%20kitchen%20sugar%20giving%20them%20the%20name%20%26quot%3Bcandy%20bombs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20portion%20of%20baking%20soda%20is%20also%20added%20to%20the%20above%20components%20and%20this%20is%20done%20to%20ensure%20the%20sugar%20and%20potassium%20nitrate%20do%20not%20catch%20fire%20but%20only%20release%20a%20thick%20coloured%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20colour%20can%20be%20any%20industrial%20dye%20available%20at%20textile%20dyeing%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20chemicals%20are%20then%20mixed%2C%20put%20inside%20a%20tube%2C%20and%20sealed%20at%20one%20end.%20From%20the%20end%20where%20the%20smoke%20emerges%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20some%20form%20of%20ignition.%20A%20simple%20lighted%20incense%20stick%20can%20be%20used%20to%20light%20the%20mixture%20which%20then%20throws%20up%20the%20coloured%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20parliament%20security%20breach%2C%20the%20canisters%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20activated%20with%20a%20pin%20mechanism%20since%20none%20of%20the%20videos%20showed%20the%20intruder%20lighting%20a%20fire.%20Also%2C%20everything%20happened%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20smoke%20bombs%20come%20in%20many%20colours%20-%20red%2C%20blue%2C%20orange%2C%20green%20or%20any%20dye%20that%20can%20be%20added%20to%20the%20mixture%20of%20potassium%20nitrate%2C%20sugar%20and%20baking%20soda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20more%20robust%20security%20system%20could%20have%20very%20easily%20detected%20these%20canisters%20if%20only%20the%20threat%20perception%20was%20anticipated%20by%20the%20many%20agencies%20manning%20the%20parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20added%20layer%20of%20foolproof%20canine%20security%20could%20have%20averted%20this%20embarrassment%20for%20the%20Indian%20security%20apparatus.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702556280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fn234us38_parliament-smoke-canister_625x300_13_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-are-candy-bombs-used-in-parliament-breach-4673392%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ominous%20yellow%20smoke%20that%20engulfed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20was%20an%20enormous%20security%20breach.%20Sometimes%20referred%20to%20as%20rocket%20candy%20bombs%2C%20these%20canisters%20are%20mostly%20benign%20and%20not%20very%20hard%20to%20put%20together%20as%20a%20do-it-yourself%20(DIY)%20exercise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-are-candy-bombs-used-in-parliament-breach-4673392%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-are-candy-bombs-used-in-parliament-breach-4673392%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-are-candy-bombs-used-in-parliament-breach-4673392%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fighter%3A%20Hrithik%20drops%20new%20song%20teaser%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702556203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105995036%2Cimgsize-35500.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdeepika-padukone-hrithik-roshan-tease-fans-with-a-glimpse-of-their-dance-number-from-fighter-set-to-release-tomorrow-watch%2Farticleshow%2F105995036.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105995036.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHrithik%20Roshan%20took%20to%20his%20social%20media%20and%20treated%20fans%20with%20a%20teaser%20of%20'Sher%20Khul%20Gaye'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdeepika-padukone-hrithik-roshan-tease-fans-with-a-glimpse-of-their-dance-number-from-fighter-set-to-release-tomorrow-watch%2Farticleshow%2F105995036.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20%E2%80%98Running%20Away%E2%80%99%20With%20Strategically%20Important%20Advanced%20Industries%3A%20Think%20Tank%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F31140436%2Fimage-871.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20China%20has%20grown%20to%20be%20the%20leading%20producer%20in%20most%20advanced-technology%20industries%20of%20strategic%20importance%2C%20the%20US-based%20Information%20Technology%20%26amp%3B%20Innovation%20Foundation%20(ITIF)%20think%20tank%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EITIF%20highlighted%20that%20China%E2%80%99s%20rise%20has%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20US%20and%20other%20OECD%20economies%2C%20and%20added%20that%20China%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20outperform%20in%20these%20key%20industries%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20decrease%20in%20manufacturing%20growth%20experienced%20by%20developing%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20findings%20are%20published%20in%20ITIF%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.itif.org%2F2023-hamilton-index.pdf%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20titled%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hamilton%20Index%2C%202023%3A%20China%20is%20Running%20Away%20With%20Strategic%20Industries%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0released%20on%20Wednesday%20(December%2013).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamilton%20Index%20ranks%20the%20performance%20of%20countries%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20output%20in%20ten%20advanced-technology%20industries%2C%20including%20IT%20services%2C%20computer%20and%20electronic%20products%2C%20transport%20equipment%2C%20machinery%2C%20pharmaceuticals%20and%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ITIF%2C%20China%20was%20the%20leading%20producer%20overall%20in%20these%20ten%20industries%20as%20of%202020%20and%20individually%20in%20seven.%20The%20US%20led%20production%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98IT%20and%20information%20services%E2%80%99%2C%20pharmaceuticals%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fitif.org%2Fpublications%2F2023%2F12%2F13%2F2023-hamilton-index%2F%23_Appendices%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98other%20transportation%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20produced%20a%20quarter%20(25.3%25)%20of%20the%20global%20output%20in%20these%20industries%2C%20the%20highest%20of%20any%20individual%20country%2C%20ITIF%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20its%20output%20had%20surpassed%20that%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20outside%20the%20top%2010%20producers%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20share%20of%20the%20global%20output%20in%20these%20industries%20increased%20from%203%25%20in%201995%20to%2025%25%20in%202020%2C%20while%20in%20the%20same%20period%2C%20the%20share%20of%20OECD%20economies%20fell%20from%2085%25%20to%2058%25%2C%20ITIF%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ffrom-1960-to-1990-india-and-china-were-at-par-how-did-it-then-overtake-us%5C%22%3EFrom%201960%20to%201990%2C%20India%20and%20China%20Were%20at%20Par.%20How%20Did%20It%20Then%20Overtake%20Us%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20ten%20industries%E2%80%99%20collective%20global%20output%20has%20represented%20a%20similar%20share%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20economy%20for%20the%20last%2025%20years%2C%20which%20it%20said%20%E2%80%9Cunderscores%20the%20zero-sum%20competition%20between%20nations%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20in%20other%20words%2C%20that%20when%20one%20country%20increased%20its%20share%2C%20others%20lost%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Asian%20giant%E2%80%99s%20strongest%20performance%20was%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98basic%20metals%E2%80%99%2C%20machine%20equipment%2C%20and%20computers%20and%20electronics%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20considering%20the%20Hamilton%20index%20industries%20other%20than%20%E2%80%98IT%20and%20information%20services%E2%80%99%20between%202017%20and%202020%2C%20Chinese%20output%20increased%20by%20%24363%20billion%20while%20that%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20fell%20by%20%24107%20billion%2C%20the%20think%20tank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14165252%2Fimage009.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14165252%2Fimage009.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14165252%2Fimage009-300x188.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689199%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENominal%20change%20in%20advanced%20industry%20output%20from%202017%20to%202020%2C%20China%20vs.%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20Chart%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fitif.org%2Fpublications%2F2023%2F12%2F13%2F2023-hamilton-index%2F%5C%22%3EInformation%20Technology%20and%20Innovation%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%2FCreative%20Commons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20IT%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20industries%20identified%20by%20ITIF%20where%20China%20lags%20behind%2C%20as%20is%20the%20pharmaceuticals%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20that%20%5BChina%E2%80%99s%20outperformance%20in%20these%20sectors%5D%20might%20not%20last%2C%20as%20the%20Chinese%20government%20has%20targeted%20biopharmaceuticals%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20as%20key%20industries%20for%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%E2%80%99s%20authors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20OECD%20grouping%2C%20the%20ITIF%20said%20that%20the%20market%20share%20of%20the%20G7%20countries%20in%20the%20Hamilton%20index%20industries%20dipped%20as%20well%2C%20decreasing%20by%20close%20to%2028%20percentage%20points%20between%201995%20and%202020.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20share%20went%20up%20by%2021.9%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20developing%20world%2C%20ITIF%20said%20although%20global%20production%20in%20all%20ten%20industries%20has%20shifted%20away%20from%20OECD%20countries%20in%20the%2025%20years%20in%20consideration%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20growth%20made%20up%20the%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20the%20non-OECD%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20gain%20has%20come%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20expense%20of%20most%20of%20the%20developing%20world%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20report%20added%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20manufacturing%20growth%20in%20developing%20countries%20has%20slowed%20or%20stagnated%20since%20China%E2%80%99s%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchina-middle-class-growth-gdp-world%5C%22%3EWhat%20Will%20a%20Continued%20Growth%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20Middle%20Class%20Mean%20For%20the%20Rest%20of%20the%20World%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Can%20India%20get%20out%20of%20its%20own%20way%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20ITIF%E2%80%99s%20report%20profiles%20India%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20ten%20producers%20in%20the%20Hamilton%20index%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20think%20tank%20noted%20that%20while%20India%20exceeded%20China%E2%80%99s%20workforce%2C%20its%20advanced%20industry%20output%20was%20only%2013%25%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%3B%20and%20that%20China%20has%20exceeded%20India%E2%80%99s%20advanced%20industry%20output%20due%20to%20long-standing%20development%20policies%2C%20which%20India%20has%20lacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20said%20that%20while%20%E2%80%9Cvirtually%20every%20nation%20in%20the%20world%20must%20fight%20and%20claw%20to%20gain%20global%20market%20share%20and%20momentum%2C%E2%80%9D%20India%20might%20be%20the%20only%20country%20that%20%E2%80%9Csimply%20must%20get%20out%20of%20its%20own%20way%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%E2%80%99s%20authors%20explained%20that%20India%20could%20emerge%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20China%20and%20reap%20high%20foreign%20investment%20if%20it%20%E2%80%98assured%20the%20basics%E2%80%99%20to%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20India%20could%20assure%20investors%20of%20the%20basics%20(working%20infrastructure%3B%20a%20pro-business%20climate%20including%20reasonable%20taxes%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20trade%20policy%2C%20and%20a%20modestly%20skilled%20workforce)%2C%20then%20the%20advantages%20it%20enjoys%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20China%20that%20is%20large%20and%20has%20low%20wages%20should%20lead%20to%20massive%20inward%20foreign%20investment%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20three%20strongest%20performing%20industries%20relative%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20were%20the%20basic%20metals%2C%20IT%20services%20and%20pharmaceuticals%20industries%2C%20where%20its%20share%20of%20the%20global%20output%20was%20higher%20than%20the%20global%20average%20share%2C%20ITIF%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14165459%2FIndia-Hamilton-industries.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14165459%2FIndia-Hamilton-industries.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14165459%2FIndia-Hamilton-industries-300x119.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14165459%2FIndia-Hamilton-industries-1024x407.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689200%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22477%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20relative%20performance%20in%20Hamilton%20Index%20industries%20(2020%20LQ).%20A%20value%20of%201.1%20means%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20global%20output%20for%20that%20industry%20is%20110%25%20the%20expected%20level.%20Chart%3A%20Information%20Technology%20and%20Innovation%20Foundation%2FCreative%20Commons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weakest%20three%20out%20of%20the%20ten%20Hamilton%20industries%20were%20computers%20and%20electronics%3B%20fabricated%20metals%3B%20and%20machinery%20and%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702555864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F31140436%2Fimage-871.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%