ancelled%20the%20press%20conference%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalled%20'Direct%20Line%20with%20Vladimir%20Putin'%2C%20the%20event%20is%20a%20carefully%20orchestrated%20and%20curated%20affair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20peace%20when%20we%20achieve%20our%20goals.%20Let's%20return%20to%20these%20goals%20-%20they%20have%20not%20changed.%20I'll%20remind%20you%20of%20what%20we%20talked%20about%20then%20-%20the%20denazification%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20its%20demilitarisation%2C%20its%20neutral%20status%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Russian%20President%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20for%20demilitarisation%2C%20if%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20come%20to%20an%20agreement%2C%20then%20we%20are%20forced%20to%20take%20other%20measures%2C%20including%20military%20ones.%20Or%20we%20will%20agree%20on%20certain%20terms.%20By%20the%20way%20we%20agreed%20on%20these%20in%20talks%20in%20Istanbul.%20But%20then%20these%20agreements%20were%20scrapped.%20But%20we%20agreed%20on%20this.%20There%20are%20other%20possibilities%20-%20either%20reach%20an%20agreement%20or%20resolve%20it%20by%20force.%20This%20is%20what%20we%20will%20strive%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FInternational%2FwireStory%2Fputin-taking-questions-ordinary-russians-journalists-reelection-bid-105649014%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20Mr%20Putin%20offered%20rare%20details%20on%20Moscow's%20operation%2C%20saying%20there%20are%20some%20617%2C000%20Russian%20soldiers%20currently%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20including%20around%20244%2C000%20troops%20who%20were%20called%20up%20to%20fight%20alongside%20professional%20Russian%20military%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20had%20opened%20lines%20for%20ordinary%20Russians%20to%20submit%20questions%20for%20the%20President%20along%20with%20those%20asked%20by%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20one%20and%20a%20half%20million%20questions%20have%20been%20submitted%2C%20Russian%20state%20media%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Russia's%20economy%2C%20Mr%20Putin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20indicator%20is%20economic%20growth.%20GDP%20growth%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20is%20expected%20at%203.5%20per%20cent%20-%20this%20is%20a%20good%20indicator%2C%20it%20means%20we%20have%20recovered%20from%20last%20year's%20fall...%20and%20we%20have%20made%20a%20relatively%20seriously%20step%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20inflation%20has%20increased.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20it%20is%20expected%20at%207.5%20per%20cent%2C%20maybe%20a%20little%20more%20at%208%20per%20cent%2C%20but%20the%20central%20bank%20and%20government%20are%20taking%20necessary%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Russian%20President%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20is%20being%20held%20in%20Gostiny%20Dvor%2C%20a%20historic%20market%20space%20now%20used%20as%20an%20exhibition%20and%20conference%20hall%2C%20close%20to%20Red%20Square%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F12%2F14%2Fputin-news-conference-reelection-war%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStringent%20security%20measures%20have%20been%20put%20in%20place%20and%20attendees%20asked%20to%20pass%20through%20four%20checkpoints.%20They%20were%20also%20given%20a%20list%20of%2026%20banned%20items%2C%20including%20Nazi%20symbols%2C%20flags%2C%20aerosols%2C%20radioactive%20devices%2C%20toxic%20chemicals%2C%20household%20chemicals%2C%20narcotics%2C%20animals%2C%20drones%2C%20bicycles%2C%20food%2C%20and%20water%20bottles%2C%20as%20well%20as%20weapons%2C%20explosives%20and%20pyrotechnics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702554600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fef7e3qq_vladimir-putin-afp-_625x300_08_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fat-annual-year-end-pres