%20classic%20case%20of%20an%20Indian%20cricket%20talent%2C%20who%20rose%20from%20a%20small%20town%20to%20the%20highest%20echelons%20of%20the%20sport.%20Hailing%20from%20Amroha%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%20never%20had%20it%20easy.%20But%20he%20played%20state%20level%20cricket%20for%20Bengal%20before%20making%20it%20big%20in%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%C2%A0Mohammed%20Shami%20was%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20performers%20at%20the%20ODI%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%20With%2024%20wickets%2C%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20fast%20bowler%20was%20the%20most%20successful%20bowler%20at%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20a%20phase%20where%20Mohammed%20Shami%20wanted%20to%20die%20by%20suicide.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20revealed%20in%20an%20instagram%20live%20chat%20with%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20that%20phase.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20my%20family%20had%20not%20supported%20me%20back%20then%20I%20would%20have%20lost%20my%20cricket.%20I%20thought%20of%20committing%20suicide%20three%20times%20during%20that%20period%20due%20to%20severe%20stress%20and%20personal%20problems.%20I%20was%20not%20thinking%20about%20cricket%20at%20all.%20We%20were%20living%20on%20the%2024th%20floor%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohammed%20Shami%20had%20said%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20scared%20I%20might%20jump%20from%20the%20balcony.%20My%202-3%20friends%20used%20to%20stay%20with%20me%20for%2024%20hours.%20My%20parents%20asked%20me%20to%20focus%20on%20cricket%20to%20recover%20from%20that%20phase%20and%20not%20think%20about%20anything%20else.%20I%20started%20training%20then%20and%20sweated%20it%20out%20a%20lot%20at%20an%20academy%20in%20Dehradun.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20still%20thinks%20about%20that%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20had%20said%20that%20'there%20was%20a%20phase%20in%20my%20life%2C%20where%20I%20wanted%20to%20die%20by%20suicide'.%20Do%20you%20now%20look%20back%20and%20think%20what%20really%20happened%20that%20you%20made%20such%20a%20big%20statement%3F%26quot%3B%20Mohammed%20Shami%20was%20asked%20by%20the%20anchor%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1b89RlmBYBw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAaj%20Tak%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20about%20it.%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20need%20to%20think.%20very%20person%20goes%20thorugh%20such%20pahse.%20I%20think%20now%20that%20it%20was%20such%20a%20bad%20phase.%20It%20was%20a%20bad%20time.%20I%20don't%20think%20about%20that%20phase.%20I%20live%20in%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohammed%20Shami%20replied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%20opened%20up%20in%20detail%20about%20his%20'disturbed'%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAapke%20life%20mein%20bahut%20difficult%20times%20bhi%20rahe%20hai.%20You%20have%20talked%20openly%20about%20mental%20health.%20It's%20a%20good%20thing.%20Jab%20aap%20mental%20health%20ke%20uss%20daur%20se%20guzar%20rahe%20the%2C%20thode%20issues%20the%2C%20aapke%20life%20ka%20difficult%20time%20tha%2C%20to%20aapke%20andar%20kya%20chal%20raha%20tha%20uss%20time%20pe%3C%2Fem%3E%20(What%20were%20thinking%20when%20you%20were%20going%20through%20difficult%20times%2C%20when%20you%20had%20issues)%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20anchor%20asked%20Mohammed%20Shami%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20an%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EShuru%20main%20to%20bahut%20difficult%20tha%2C%20because%20mere%20family%20mein%20aisa%20kuch%20hua%20hi%20nahi.%20Koi%20jhamela%20nahi.%3C%2Fem%3E%20(It%20was%20tough%20in%20the%20beginning%20because%20nothing%20of%20such%20sort%20has%20happened%20in%20my%20life).%20We%20have%20a%20simple%20family.%20It%20was%20difficult%20time%2C%20stressful%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohammed%20Shami%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAgar%20aap%20jhoothe%20ho%20to%20aap%20bhagoge%2C%20aapko%20pata%20hai.%20Agar%20aapko%20lagta%20hai%20ki%20aap%20galat%20ho%20to%20aap%20aankh%20hi%20nahi%20milaoge.%20Maine%20bola%20thik%20hai%20aur%20lagaane%20do%20bhai.%20Jo%20sach%20hai%20woh%20mil%20jayega%20aapko.%20Maine%20bola%20kahaan%20bulana%20hai%20mujhe%20kahaan%20aana%20hai.%20Sari%20cheez%20dekh%20li%3C%2Fem%3E%20(If%20your%20are%20a%20liar%20you%20will%20run%20away.%20I%20always%20believed%20that%20truth%20will%20come%20out.%20I%20told%20I%20will%20go%20anywhere%20I%20am%20called.%20I%20have%20seen%20everything).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702553880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fb3vfsmi_mohammed-shami_625x300_15_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammed-shami-asked-about-phase-where-he-wanted-to-die-by-suicide-he-said-4668963%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Shami%20is%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20an%20Indian%20cricket%20talent%2C%20who%20rose%20from%20a%20small%20town%20to%20the%20highest%20echelons%20of%20the%20sport%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammed-shami-asked-about-phase-where-he-wanted-to-die-by-suicide-he-said-4668963%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammed-shami-asked-about-phase-where-he-wanted-to-die-by-suicide-he-said-4668963%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammed-shami-asked-about-phase-where-he-wanted-to-die-by-suicide-he-said-4668963%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pawan%20Munjal-backed%20Exponent%20raises%20%2426.4%20million%20in%20Series%20B%20round%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702553767000%2C