-will-be-no-peace-until-theyre-achieved-13030165%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvladimir-putin-says-ukraine-war-goals-are-unchanged-and-there-will-be-no-peace-until-theyre-achieved-13030165%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvladimir-putin-says-ukraine-war-goals-are-unchanged-and-there-will-be-no-peace-until-theyre-achieved-13030165%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Fertility%20Doctor%20Accused%20Of%20Secretly%20Impregnating%20Woman%20With%20Own%20Sperm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20retired%20fertility%20doctor%20from%20Boston%20is%20being%20sued%20by%20a%20woman%20who%20alleged%20that%20he%20used%20his%20own%20sperm%20to%20impregnate%20her%20more%20than%2040%20years%20ago%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2023%2Fdec%2F13%2Fboston-fertility-doctor-accused-impregnating-patient-own-sperm-iui%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAccording%2520to%2520a%2520civil%2520claim%2Cwho%2520had%2520been%2520seeking%2520intrauterine%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0According%20to%20a%20civil%20claim%20filed%20in%20US%20district%20court%20in%20Boston%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Dr.%20Merle%20Berger%2C%20one%20of%20the%20founders%20of%20Boston%20IVF%20and%20a%20former%20professor%20at%20Harvard%20Medical%20School%2C%C2%A0secretly%20impregnated%20a%20patient%20named%20Sarah%20Depoia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Depoian%20explained%20that%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20went%20to%20Dr.%20Merle%20Berger%20in%201980%20for%20help%20getting%20pregnant.%20Dr%20Berger%20told%20her%20the%20sperm%20would%20come%20from%20an%20anonymous%20donor%20''who%20resembled%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20did%20not%20know%20her%2C%20and%20whom%20she%20did%20not%20know.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%C2%A0Mrs%20Depoian%20claims%20that%20the%20doctor%20used%20his%20sperm%20and%20impregnated%20her.%20Her%20daughter%2C%20Carolyn%20Bester%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20insemination%2C%20was%20born%20in%20January%201981.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%C2%A0Ms%20Bester%20conducted%20a%20home%20DNA%20test%20and%20discovered%20Dr%20Berger%20was%20her%20biological%20father%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%C2%A0Among%20her%20DNA%20matches%20were%20Dr%20Berger's%20granddaughter%20and%20second%20cousin%2C%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20spoke%20to%20one%20of%20them%2C%20and%20I%20started%20piecing%20it%20all%20together.%20To%20say%20I%20was%20shocked%20when%20I%20figured%20this%20out%20would%20be%20an%20extreme%20understatement.%20It%20feels%20like%20reality%20has%20shifted%2C''%20Ms%20Bester%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdam%20Wolf%2C%20a%20lawyer%20representing%20Mrs%20Depoian%2C%20said%20Dr%20Berger%20knew%20that%20what%20he%20was%20doing%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''He%20did%20so%20without%20her%20consent%20and%20against%20her%20wishes.%20Some%20people%20call%20this%20horrific%20act%20medical%20rape.%20But%20regardless%20of%20what%20you%20call%20it%2C%20Dr.%20Berger's%20heinous%20and%20intentional%20misconduct%20is%20unethical%2C%20unacceptable%2C%20and%20unlawful%2C''%20the%20woman's%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''This%20is%20an%20extreme%20violation.%20I%20am%20still%20struggling%20to%20process%20it.%20I%20trusted%20Dr%20Berger%20fully.%20We%20thought%20he%20would%20act%20responsibly%20and%20ethically%2C''%20Mrs%20Depoian%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20her%20attorneys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20Dr%20Berger's%20lawyer%20also%20released%20a%20statement%20on%20his%20behalf%3A%C2%A0%26quot%3BDr.%20Merle%20Berger%20was%20a%20pioneer%20in%20the%20medical%20fertility%20field%20who%20in%2050%20years%20of%20practice%20helped%20thousands%20of%20families%20fulfill%20their%20dreams%20of%20having%20a%20child.%20He%20is%20widely%20known%20for%20his%20sensitivity%20to%20the%20emotional%20anguish%20of%20the%20women%20who%20came%20to%20him%20for%20help%20conceiving.%20The%20allegations%20concern%20events%20from%20over%2040%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20artificial%20insemination.%20At%20a%20time%20before%20sperm%20banks%20and%20IVF%2C%20it%20was%20dramatically%20different%20from%20modern-day%20fertility%20treatment.%20The%20allegations%2C%20which%20have%20changed%20repeatedly%20in%20the%20six%20months%20since%20the%20plaintiff's%20attorney%20first%20contacted%20Dr.%20Berger%2C%20have%20no%20legal%20or%20factual%20merit%2C%20and%20will%20be%20disproven%20in%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20several%20other%20instances%20of%20fertility%20doctors%20being%20accused%20of%20using%20their%20own%20sperm%20to%20impregnate%20a%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702553520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F7qt26bo_pregnant-woman_625x300_29_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-fertility-doctor-accused-of-secretly-impregnating-woman-with-his-own-sperm-4673067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr.%20Merle%20Berger%2C%20one%20of%20the%20founders%20of%20Boston%20IVF%20and%20a%20former%20professor%20at%20Harvard%20Medical%20School%2C%20secretly%20impregnated%20a%20patient%20named%20Sarah%20Depoia%2040%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-fertility-doctor-accused-of-secretly-impregnating-woman-with-his-own-sperm-4673067%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-fertility-doctor-accused-of-secretly-impregnating-woman-with-his-own-sperm-4673067%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-fertility-doctor-accused-of-secretly-impregnating-woman-with-his-own-sperm-4673067%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%