0found%20a%20week%20later%20with%20the%20'destroyed'%20doughnuts%2C%20according%20to%20the%20police.%20The%20police%20checked%20the%20CCTV%20camera%20and%20found%20that%20a%20woman%20was%20lingering%20at%20the%20service%20station%20and%20after%20finding%20the%20driver%20unattended%2C%20she%20stole%20the%20van.%20It%20is%20still%20not%20clear%20whether%20she%20knew%20that%20there%20were%20doughnuts%20or%20not%20in%20van.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralian-woman-charged-after-stealing-van-with-10000-doughnuts%2Farticleshow%2F105992321.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Krishna%20Janmabhoomi%20Case%3A%20Allahabad%20HC%20Orders%20Survey%20of%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Mosque%20in%20Mathura%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25112937%2FSEM1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20has%20given%20its%20nod%20for%20the%20survey%20of%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Mosque%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Mathura%20by%20a%20court-appointed%20and%20monitored%20advocate%20commissioner%20in%20response%20to%20petitions%20filed%20by%20Hindutva%20outfits%20which%20claim%20that%20the%20mosque%20stands%20on%20the%20place%20where%20Lord%20Krishna%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20has%20allowed%20our%20plea%20for%20appointment%20of%20a%20commission%20to%20survey%20the%20site.%20More%20details%20will%20be%20out%20when%20the%20order%20is%20uploaded%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkrishna-janmabhoomi-land-dispute-case-allahabad-hc-survey-of-shahi-idgah-mosque-9068116%2F%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ranjana%20Agnihotri%2C%20counsel%20for%20petitioners%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20survey%20of%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%2C%20the%20survey%20of%20the%2017th-century%20mosque%20is%20to%20ascertain%20the%20claims%20being%20made%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20built%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Krishna%20Janmasthal%20(believed%20to%20be%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Krishna)%20after%20demolishing%20Katra%20Keshav%20Dev%20Temple.%20The%20temple%20side%20claims%20that%20the%20entire%20tract%20of%20contested%20land%20%E2%80%93%20about%2013.37%20acres%20%E2%80%93%20belongs%20to%20it%20and%20the%20mosque%20should%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20site.%20According%20to%20the%20petitioners%2C%20Katra%20Keshav%20Dev%20Temple%20was%20demolished%20by%20Mughal%20Emperor%20Aurangzeb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%2C%20another%20advocate%20for%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20has%20allowed%20our%20demand%20that%20an%20advocate%20commissioner%20must%20be%20appointed.%20Who%20will%20be%20the%20advocate%20commissioner%2C%20what%20will%20the%20modalities%20be%2C%20and%20whether%20it%20will%20be%20a%20three-member%20committee%3F%20All%20these%20things%20will%20be%20decided%20on%20December%2018.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20demanded%20that%20in%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20mosque%2C%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20signs%20and%20symbols%2C%20and%20to%20know%20the%20actual%20factual%20position%2C%20an%20actual%20advocate%20commissioner%20is%20required.%20The%20court%20has%20allowed%20our%20application.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2018%20separate%20pleas%20were%20filed%20in%20various%20courts%20of%20Mathura%20seeking%20full%20ownership%20of%20the%2013.37-acre%20land%20to%20the%20temple%20management.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20clubbed%20all%20pleas%20and%20transferred%20them%20to%20itself%20for%20adjudicating%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20support%20of%20their%20claims%2C%20these%20groups%20say%20that%20there%20are%20carvings%20of%20lotuses%20on%20some%20walls%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20as%20well%20as%20shapes%20supposedly%20resembling%20Sheshnag%20%E2%80%93%20the%20snake%20demigod%20in%20Hindu%20mythology.%20This%2C%20they%20say%2C%20proves%20their%20point%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20indeed%20built%20after%20demolishing%20the%20temple%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-mathuras-krishna-janmabhoomi-land-dispute-court-gives-nod-for-survey-4672258%5C%22%3ENDTV%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20side%20had%20earlier%20moved%20the%20high%20court%20praying%20for%20the%20quashing%20of%20petitions%20citing%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20of%201991%2C%20which%20maintains%20the%20religious%20status%20of%20any%20place%20of%20worship%20as%20it%20was%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20in%201968%2C%20both%20the%20temple%20side%20(Shri%20Krishna%20Janmasthan%20Seva%20Sansthan)%20and%20the%20mosque%20side%20(Shahi%20Masjid%20Idgah%20Trust)%20inked%20an%20agreement%20to%20the%20effect%20that%2010.9%20acres%20from%20the%20total%2013.37%20acres%20would%20be%20of%20the%20temple%E2%80%99s%20property%20while%202.5%20acres%20would%20belong%20to%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20side%20is%20expected%20to%20challenge%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702552516000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25112937%2FSEM1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkrishna-janmabhoomi-case-allahabad-hc-orders-survey-of-shahi-idgah-mosque-in-mathura%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20survey%20of%20the%2017th-century%20mosque%20is%20to%20ascertain%20the%20claims%20being%20made%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20built%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Krishna%20Janmasthal%20(believed%20to%20be%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Krishna)%20after%20demolishing%20Katra%20Keshav%20Dev%20Temple.%2