23121400693_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fudaan-raises-340-million-in-funding-eyes-profitability-in-12-18-months-123121400693_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Green%20Has%20Kidney%20Disease%2C%205th%20Stage%20Of%20Which%20Is%20Dialysis.%20Star%20Now%20At...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralia%20all-rounder%20Cameron%20Green%20has%20revealed%20he%20was%20born%20with%20an%20irreversible%20chronic%20kidney%20disease%2C%20which%20at%20one%20stage%20put%20his%20life%20expectancy%20at%2012%20years.%20The%20lanky%20all-rounder%2C%20who%20is%20a%20vital%20part%20of%20the%20Australia%20cricket%20team%2C%20said%20that%20the%20disease%20has%20no%20symptoms%20and%20is%20irreversible.%20%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20got%20told%20when%20I%20was%20born%20that%20I%20had%20chronic%20kidney%20disease%2C%20basically%2C%20there's%20no%20symptoms%2C%20it%20was%20just%20picked%20up%20through%20ultra%20sounds%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20told%20Channel%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChronic%20kidney%20disease%20is%20basically%20a%20progressive%20disease%20of%20your%20kidney's%20health%20function.%20Unfortunately%2C%20mine%20don't%20filter%20the%20blood%20as%20well%20as%20other%20kidneys.%26quot%3B%20The%2024-year-old%20revealed%20that%20his%20kidney%20function%20is%20currently%20at%20about%2060%20per%20cent%2C%20which%20is%20stage%20two%2C%20with%20stage%20five%20needing%20transplant%20or%20dialysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFortunately%2C%20I'm%20stage%20two%2C%20but%20if%20you%20don't%20look%20after%20them%20enough%2C%20it%20easily%20goes%20back%20down.%20Kidneys%20can't%20get%20better.%20It's%20irreversible.%20So%20any%20way%20you%20can%20find%20to%20slow%20the%20progression%2C%20you%20basically%20try%20and%20do.%26quot%3B%20The%20condition%20was%20detected%20when%20Green's%20mother%20Tarcy%20had%20her%2019-week%20pregnancy%20scan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%20it%20was%20unchartered%20territory%20as%20such%2C%20the%20prognosis%20wasn't%20great.%20There%20were%20life%20expectancy%20issues%20that%20he%20might%20not%20expect%20to%20live%20past%2012%20years%20of%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Green's%20father%2C%20Gary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fast-bowling%20all-rounder%2C%20who%20has%20featured%20in%2024%20Tests%2C%2023%20ODIs%20and%20eight%20T20Is%20since%20making%20his%20Australia%20debut%20in%202020%2C%20said%20the%20disease%20also%20affects%20his%20cricketing%20career%20as%20he%20is%20more%20susceptible%20to%20cramps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20got%20to%20keep%20my%20salt%20and%20my%20protein%20quite%20low%2C%20which%20isn't%20ideal%20as%20a%20cricketer%20but%20around%20games%20I%20can%20pick%20that%20protein%20intake%20back%20up%20because%20I%20spend%20so%20much%20of%20it%20out%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20about%20finding%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20look%20after%20me.%26quot%3B%20He%20recalled%20an%20incident%20during%20an%20ODI%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Cairns%20last%20year%2C%20where%20he%20started%20cramping%20due%20to%20the%20disease%20while%20batting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECameron%20Green%20has%20chronic%20kidney%20disease.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThere%20are%20five%20stages%20to%20it%2C%20with%20the%20fifth%20stage%20requiring%20a%20transplant%20or%20dialysis.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20is%20how%20Green%20-%20currently%20at%20stage%20two%20-%20manages%20the%20condition%20every%20day...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FikbIntapdy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FikbIntapdy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%207Cricket%20(%407Cricket)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F7Cricket%2Fstatus%2F1735159433209298971%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20definitely%20one%20time%20up%20in%20Cairns%2C%20playing%20Australia%20versus%20New%20Zealand%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20pretty%20well%20documented%20that%20I%20had%20a%20pretty%20long%20day%20of%20bowling%20and%20a%20pretty%20long%20bat%20as%20well%2C%20and%20then%20had%20a%20cramping%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%20me%20a%20long%20time%20to%20realise%20that%20it%20was%20probably%20my%20kidney%20function%20that%20was%20affecting%20my%20cramping%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20shy%20person%2C%20Green%20said%20he%20had%20to%20eventually%20tell%20his%20teammates%20about%20the%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20told%20a%20few%20guys%20in%20the%20cricket%20world.%20The%20coaching%20staff%20are%20all%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20all%20the%20guys%20in%20the%20Aussie%20cricket%20team%2C%20I've%20told.%20After%20a%20few%20cramping%20episodes%2C%20I%20probably%20had%20to%20come%20off%20and%20tell%20them%20that%20it's%20probably%20more%20than%20not%20being%20professional%20enough%20because%20I%20knew%20in%20the%20background%20I%20was%20eating%20and%20drinking%20as%20much%20as%20I%20could%20to%20give%20myself%20the%20best%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702549380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F0f0pm7v8_cameron-green-afp_625x300_11_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcameron-green-says-he-has-chronic-kidney-disease-5th-stage-of-which-is-dialysis-star-is-now-at-4672028%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20shy%20person%2C%20Cameron%20Green%20said%20he%20had%20to%20eventually%20tell%20his%20teammates%20about%20the%20condition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcameron-green-says-he-has-chronic-kidney-disease-5th-stage-of-which-is-dialysis-star-is-now-at-4672028%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com