5988638.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHungary's%20Prime%20Minister%20Viktor%20Orban%20stated%20that%20Hungary%20would%20support%20in%20providing%20long-term%20financial%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20outside%20of%20the%20EU%20budget.%20Orban%20reiterated%20his%20opposition%20to%20starting%20accession%20talks%20with%20Ukraine.%20The%20EU%20countries%2C%20excluding%20Hungary%2C%20aim%20to%20offer%20Ukraine%2050%20billion%20euros%20in%20budget%20support%20until%202027%20and%20advance%20its%20membership%20bid.%20Orban%20mentioned%20that%20there%20is%20no%20rush%20to%20decide%20on%20additional%20financial%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20as%20short-term%20support%20is%20already%20secured.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fhungary-against-eu-talks-with-ukraine-open-to-financial-aid-for-kyiv%2Farticleshow%2F105988638.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fhungary-against-eu-talks-with-ukraine-open-to-financial-aid-for-kyiv%2Famp_articleshow%2F105988638.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fhungary-against-eu-talks-with-ukraine-open-to-financial-aid-for-kyiv%2Famp_articleshow%2F105988638.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jackie%20Shroff%20to%20play%20baddie%20in%20Varun%20Dhawan's%20next%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702546814000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105989566%2Cimgsize-80168.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjackie-shroff-to-play-baddie-in-varun-dhawans-next%2Farticleshow%2F105989616.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105989616.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJackie%20Shroff%2C%20known%20