D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2023-03-17%2Fexplainer-incendiary-weapons-in-ukraine%2F102093560%5C%22%3Eamong%20the%20cruelest%20weapons%20used%20in%20contemporary%20armed%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20their%20impact%20on%20the%20human%20body.%20Says%20one%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20researcher%3A%20%E2%80%9CIncendiary%20weapons%20are%20weapons%20that%20set%20fire%20or%20burn%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20phosphorus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jurist.org%2Fcommentary%2F2014%2F12%2Fsascha-dominikbachmann-incendiary-weapons%2F%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20used%3C%2Fa%3E%20defensively%2C%20though%2C%20as%20a%20smokescreen%20to%20mask%20troop%20movements%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20to%20illuminate%20the%20battlefield%2C%20or%20as%20a%20signalling%20device.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F12%2Fquestions-and-answers-israels-use-white-phosphorus-gaza-and-lebanon%5C%22%3Ecan%20also%20interfere%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20enemy%E2%80%99s%20infrared%20optics%20and%20weapons%20tracking%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20incendiary%20weapons%20can%20also%20be%20used%20offensively%20in%20mortar%20bombs%2C%20rockets%2C%20and%20artillery%20ammunition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20phosphorous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F10%2F13%2Fwhite-phosphorus-chemical-what-is%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20used%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20many%20adversaries%20in%20both%20the%20First%20and%20Second%20World%20Wars%2C%20targeting%20enemy%20soldiers%20and%20civilians%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20also%20used%20white%20phosphorus%2C%20alongside%20napalm%2C%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20and%20more%20recently%20in%20Iraq%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2005%2Fnov%2F16%2Firaq.usa%5C%22%3Ebattle%20of%20Fallujah%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202004%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2023%2F10%2F19%2Fwhite-phosphorus-israel-ga