arls.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334696%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20group%20of%20farmers%20was%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20by%20selling%208%2C000%20pearls.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHarvesting%20pearls%20in%20water-scarce%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20pursuing%20a%20Diploma%20in%20Medical%20Laboratory%20Technology%20(DMLT)%2C%20Sanjay%20works%20part-time%20as%20a%20lab%20assistant.%20But%20farming%20comes%20naturally%20to%20him%20as%20for%20generations%2C%20his%20family%20has%20been%20cultivating%20traditional%20crops.%20However%2C%20agriculture%20hardly%20reaped%20the%20family%20any%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20year%2C%20we%20did%20not%20get%20rain%20at%20all.%20We%20did%20sow%20soybeans%20and%20other%20crops%2C%20but%20we%20did%20not%20get%20any%20output.%20It%20has%20become%20difficult%20to%20even%20earn%20back%20the%20input%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20back%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20even%20established%20a%20water%20bank%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20for%20irrigation%20purposes.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20fish%20farming%20to%20utilise%20the%20water%20bank%20but%20the%20initiative%20was%20dead%20in%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3